f whether they are receiving an acetylcholinesterase inhibitor.', 'Moderate', 'pharmacodynamic', NULL, 'https://ddinter2.scbdd.com/server/interact/188171/', '', 'Citalopram, Sertraline, Fluoxetine, St. John''s Wort, Milnacipran, Vortioxetine, Levomilnacipran, Duloxetine, Isocarboxazid, Viloxazine, Esketamine, More', 'Methazolamide, Neostigmine, Pilocarpine, Diclofenamide, Travoprost, Brinzolamide, Brimonidine, Levobunolol, Hydroxocobalamin, Fomepizole, Ipecac, More', 1767369485);
